        "committer": {
          "name": "Alex Zhuravlev",
          "email": "alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com",
          "date": "2012-10-18 12:30:42.000000000",
          "tz": 240
        },
        "subject": "LU-2138 osp: set expiration before RPC is sent",
        "message": "LU-2138 osp: set expiration before RPC is sent\n\nosp_statfs_update() should set opd_statfs_fresh_till before\nthe request is sent. otherwise the race is possible when\ninterpret function is called sooner than osp_statfs_update()\nsets opd_statfs_fresh_till to \"disable\" value. the race can\nresult in suspened statfs updates misguiding the object\nallocation algorithm.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I2ff03a611267292d0cd6a465c1eb14023516234b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
